{"tid":905742,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"又黎推廣下原創Whatsapp Sticker，今次係貓呀！","createTime":"2018-11-17T11:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T08:36:45.000Z","uid":220840,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"17d6b6958bceb99efa8ec57490f830aba7706108","tid":905742,"uid":220840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqTLUYB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqTLUYB.png&h=9c53b7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又係滿滿既30張，希望啱各位心水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw相信大家都留意到Whatsapp貼圖係會將2張相連發放既貼圖縮係同一行，今次既貓貼圖其實可以同上輯既熊貓貼圖一齊搭配使用：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WdSs8iH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWdSs8iH.png&h=f916fd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAndroid手機步驟：<br />\n1. 先在手機安裝WhatSticker app：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=online.whatsticker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Donline.whatsticker&d=%2FffIv5uq8TfcL3mG%2FY4yqI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f8219caf\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=online.whatsticker</a><br />\n2️. 到此網址點擊「Add to Android」：<a href=\"https://whatsticker.online/pack/64176kgdBbRn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatsticker.online%2Fpack%2F64176kgdBbRn&d=%2FffIv5uq8TfcL3mG%2FY4yqI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6cc7f000\" target=\"_blank\">https://whatsticker.online/pack/64176kgdBbRn</a><br />\n3. 新增到你既Whatsapp入面使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得左<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\niPhone手機步驟：(暫時只發送不良貓可可系列，如要熊貓請講聲哦)<br />\nWhatsapp群組免費索取貼圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/C59ldCvct4F0Y2JWiFUTHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchat.whatsapp.com%2FC59ldCvct4F0Y2JWiFUTHQ&d=%2FffIv5uq8TfcL3mG%2FY4yqI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0d730a56\" target=\"_blank\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/C59ldCvct4F0Y2JWiFUTHQ</a><br />\n(需要各位逐張手動保存，iPhone, android同樣適用)<br />\n<br />\n注意：<br />\n1️. 因為會一次性發30張圖⚠️，請大家係安全既環境下先入group (或者去關手機既通知)<br />\n2️. 基本上只要見到就會盡快出圖俾入group既各位，有野做時會遲少少，等下就一定有既 (有時專心打機，忽略你太耐既話可以出聲提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n3️. 過左夜晚11點要等明日先出<br />\n4️. 拎完貼圖既朋友可以自退 (因為若無更新都係重覆出一樣既30張)<br />\n5️. 貼圖可隨意使用但不得作商業/宣傳用途，用黎幫手宣傳小妹專頁除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6️. 鍾意哩系列貼圖，唔想錯過更新就快D讚好同追蹤我既Facebook page啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上輯熊貓Sticker網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://whatsticker.online/pack/24096bp9b5xe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatsticker.online%2Fpack%2F24096bp9b5xe&d=%2FffIv5uq8TfcL3mG%2FY4yqI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=bb253f95\" target=\"_blank\">https://whatsticker.online/pack/24096bp9b5xe</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8c8jZqw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8c8jZqw.png&h=4cb0870c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家得閒可以支持下小妹既創作之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pandakolala/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpandakolala%2F&d=%2FffIv5uq8TfcL3mG%2FY4yqI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fe756a9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pandakolala/</a> <br />\n點個小小既讚，對我就係莫大既鼓勵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7c651701138983386f08aafb944f72ffd6ef67","tid":905742,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"已經冇心機逐張加，雖然好cute<br />\n所以幫樓主推下post就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5b64e6cab7098d078225f4c9f02e61377f24d3","tid":905742,"uid":163554,"like":0,"