i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjuUPfOr.png&h=3ed3f8d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貓：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GX190fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGX190fb.png&h=5631d7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp群都會繼續運作(方便唔想下載三方app既人)，只係呢排煲新game可能會遲少少先覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}